1. Keep widgets small and focused
2. Use const constructors when possible
3. Implement proper widget keys when needed
4. Follow proper layout principles with responsive design
5. Use proper widget lifecycle methods
6. Implement proper error boundaries
7. Use proper performance optimization techniques
8. Follow proper accessibility guidelines
9. Use flutter_screenutil for responsive sizing
10. Prefer SizedBox over Container for whitespace
`;

